    "body": "I am not doing any url syncs. I am normally getting the slugs from `this.props.params.slug` to find slug and use this in instantsearch like this in my `render()`\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\n<InstantSearch appId={ALGOLIA_APPID}\r\n                apiKey={ALGOLIA_APIKEY}\r\n                indexName={LOWESTINDEX}\r\n                searchParameters={{\r\n                    distinct: false,\r\n                    filters: `slug: ${slug} AND instock: 1`\r\n                }}>\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen this slug changes, I need to get the new slug. \r\n\r\n```jsx\r\ncomponentWillReceiveProps(nextProps) {\r\n    if(this.props.params.slug !== nextProps.params.slug){\r\n      \r\n   // Change the state here.... and have Instantsearch take the new slug. \r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI am not sure if I can provide a working jsbin example or not. If the above description is not clear, I can try to do it. \r\n",
